        &kp LC(A)   &kp C_VOLUME_DOWN  &kp C_VOL_UP      &kp C_MUTE  &tbmcro      &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN   &kp UP           &kp RIGHT  &kp SINGLE_QUOTE
&trans  &kp LC(Z)   &kp LC(X)          &kp LC(C)         &kp LC(V)   &kp LCTRL    &kp END       &kp PRINTSCREEN  &kp LC(S)          &kp KP_NUMLOCK &kp LS(MINUS) &kp LS(N1)
                                       &kp LG(LC(LEFT))  &trans      &trans       &trans        &trans           &kp LG(LC(RIGHT))
